com.ctb.control.testAdmin
Interface TestSessionStatus

All Superinterfaces:
com.bea.control.Control, java.io.Serializable
public interface TestSessionStatus
extends com.bea.control.Control

Platform control provides functions related to test session monitoring and status, including methods to obtain lists of test sessions of interest to a particular user.

Author:
Nate_Cohen, John_Wang

getUserDetails

public User getUserDetails(java.lang.String userName,
                           java.lang.String detailUserName)
                    throws CTBBusinessException
Get user information including full name and system id for the specified user name. If the specified user lies withing the requesting user's visible hierarchy, all fields are returned - if not, only the first, last, and middle names of the specified user are returned. Each user object contains a Customer object, which contains information about the user's customer, including a flag, hideAccommodations, which indicates whether accommodation-related UI elements should be hidden for the specified user.

Parameters:
userName - - identifies the calling user
detailUserName - - identifies the user whose information is desired
Returns:
User
Throws:
CTBBusinessException
